703944f-a.title: Brooklyn: Debevoise Avenue - Maspeth Avenue
703944f-a.text:
Debevoise Ave., at the N.E. corner of Maspeth Ave. These homes faoinp on Maspeth Ave., housed the employees of Peter Cooper, who conducted a ghe factory in the rear of these houses. (Cooper Park and Cooper Union were
named in his memory.
1922.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
